cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - This paper focuses on generating coherent and diverse sentences for visual storytelling, which falls under the domain of natural language processing. 
2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper deals with generating stories from a sequence of images, which involves analyzing and understanding visual content. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a novel method for generating diverse and expressive stories, which is a key area of research in AI. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses neural network models for image to text generation, which is a common application of machine learning. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper involves generating textual content from visual input, which can be seen as a form of information retrieval.
